Subprog AS_RSKWRK(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(45608,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_RSKWRK(VALEUR) From SUBCTR
If mkstat=2
 [M]RSKWRK(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo RSKWRK(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_RSKWRK(zc) From W1CTR2
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_RSKWRK(zc) From W1CTR2
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_RSKWRK(zc) From W1CTR2
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_RSKWRK(zc) From W1CTR2
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog C_RSKWRK(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
## Action %CNTOBJ
Call CONTSEL("VAC","!",VALEUR,"",mkstat) From CONTOBJ
